      <title>卢拉削减开支计划获国会最终批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/brazil-congress-further-dilutes-lula-s-spending-cut-package</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过一周的深夜投票，巴西参议院批准了削弱版的政府支出削减方案，旨在缓解投资者对该国财政状况恶化的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/brazil-congress-further-dilutes-lula-s-spending-cut-package</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 20:50:28 GMT</pubDate>
